title: Factory Employment, Furniture and Fixtures for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1919-1942 (2)--Original Data, 1947-1957. Source: Bureau Of Labor Statistics, For 1947-1952 Data: "Employment, Hours, And Earnings", Manufacturing Division, Durable Goods Subdivision, Furniture And Fixtures, Releases Ls53-2079 And Ls54-3712, February 1953 And May 1955; For 1953-1957 Data:"Employment And Earnings, " June 1956 And Following Issues (See Also The Summary In Loose Leaf Binder Volume).
